data.title: Blackrock's iShares bitcoin fund sees record exodus as crypto heads for worst month since 2022
data.description: Blackrock's spot bitcoin ETF has so far seen $2.2 billion worth of outflows in November as its underlying crypto continues to crater.
data.author: Liz Napolitano
data.keywords: Markets,Breaking News: Markets,Stock markets,Investment strategy,Wall Street,Bitcoin/USD Coin Metrics,Ishares Bitcoin Trust,business news
